# Testing Policy

## Requirements
- Check .harness/config.json for configured test frameworks
- Every unit that adds or modifies behavior must have corresponding tests
- Tests must be specific and targeted, not broad catch-all suites

## E2E
- E2E tests are tied to phases, not individual units
- Prefer targeted E2E per phase over monolithic all-the-time suites
- Distinguish local E2E confidence from deployed E2E truth

## Evidence
- Test output must be recorded as validation evidence
- Format: "test_file passes (N/N)" or "test_file fails (N/M, failures: ...)"
